author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Integrated Says HY ‍Net Profit Attributable Up 20% To $9.3 Mln
text:
Feb 15 (Reuters) - Integrated Research Ltd:
* HY ‍NET PROFIT FOR PERIOD ATTRIBUTABLE UP 20% TO $9.3 MILLION​
* ‍HY REVENUES FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES UP 5% TO $45.7 MILLION​
* ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND 3.0 CENTS PER SECURITY​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
